
---

### `.env.example`

```env
# Local LM Studio (OpenAI-compatible)
LM_STUDIO_URL=http://localhost:1234/v1/chat/completions

# Cloud LLMs
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_key
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_key
GROK_API_KEY=your_grok_key
PPLX_API_KEY=your_perplexity_key

# Memory
MEMORY_DB_PATH=memory/store.sqlite

# Home ecosystem (optional)
HOME_ROUTER_URL=http://neuralhome:9000
HOME_NODE_RED_URL=http://neuralhome:1880

# Internal router URL
ROUTER_URL=http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions

